    <div class="article">
     <img alt="" src="images/ECi_M1.png" />
     <h4>
     </h4>
     <div class="clear">
     </div>
     <p>
      ECi M1 is an Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) software solution designed for growing manufacturers. Our customers include job shops, custom and mixed-mode manufacturers, and make-to-order manufacturers.
     </p>
     <p>
      M1 automates and integrates every business process from quoting through invoicing and point of sale (POS). It is also flexible and easy to customize, so it can handle the most valuable and unique business processes with ease.
     </p>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
     <a href="about.php">
      <img alt="" src="images/globe.jpg" />
      about
     </a>
    </div>
   </div>
   <div class="footer">
    <div style="background:none" class="section">
     <h3>
      Consulting
     </h3>
     <p>
      We provide organizational change management assistance, organizational readiness assessment, strategy development or operational improvement services.
					When M1 is not a fit for your organization, our team has many years of experience in helping you to get ready, plan your requirements, state your requirements,
					evaluate proposals and select the best fit for your organization.
     </p>
    </div>
    <div class="featured">
     <h3>
      ERP Software
     </h3>
     <p>
      We sell, implement, train, customize and support ECI | M1 as the Canadian Reseller.
					It is the only system we sell as we feel it is the best of breed for Canadian Manufacturers who are Discrete Manufacturers, Engineer to Order, Design to Order and Make to Order companies.
					M1 offers companies an opportunity to replace their current system with an up to date fairly priced system that will meet their demands for years to come.
     </p>
    </div>
    <div style="background:none" class="section">
     <h3>
      Mapping
     </h3>
     <p>
      Business process review, business process mapping and work flows are being missed by most small to medium companies.
					Ensure your future and let us help you create your own go forward documentation.
     </p>
